 <datafield tag="520" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
  <subfield code="a">We discuss the unitarity of the quantum evolution between arbitrary Cauchy surfaces of a 1  +  1 dimensional free scalar field defined on a bounded spatial region and subject to several types of boundary conditions including Dirichlet, Neumann and Robin.</subfield>
